name: libimread
tagline: Binary image read/write format support for Halide and CoreGraphics
body:
libimread
=========

Binary image read/write format support for [Halide](http://halide-lang.org) and [Apple CoreGraphics](https://developer.apple.com/library/prerelease/mac/documentation/CoreGraphics/Reference/CoreGraphicsConstantsRef/). Originally dervived from the [imread](https://github.com/luispedro/imread) C++ Python extension module source by Luis Pedro.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
